    "version": "1.0.2",
    "category": "tts",
    "name": "ElevenLabs 语音合成",
    "summary": "使用 ElevenLabs 的高质量 AI 语音朗读文本，支持自定义音色与克隆音色。",
    "author": "poyih",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/poyih/bob-plugin-11labs-tts",
